description:
Can jazz unite a community?  Bassist, Composer, Arranger, and Educator, Christian McBride, believes music can bring different people together through their love of jazz..  He talks to Steve about the TD Moody Democracy of Jazz Festival and performs ""Straight No Chaser"" by Thelonious Monk, accompanied by Pianist Oscar Perez.

Musician Southside Johnny of Southside Johnny & The Asbury Jukes talks with Steve about his passion for making music for over 40 years, what life was like growing up in Ocean Grove, and  how this New Jersey artist has used his bulldog tenacity to stay in the forefront of the music scene. 

12/19/14
